                "invention-title": [
                    "Reactor, reaction system and method for denitrification coupling polyhydroxyalkanoate synthesis based on hydrogen energy",
                    "基于氢能的反硝化耦合聚羟基脂肪酸酯合成的反应器、反应系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a reactor, a reaction system and a method for denitrifying and coupling polyhydroxyalkanoate based on hydrogen energy. The reactor comprises: a membrane bundle composed of a plurality of polypropylene polyurethane composite hollow fiber membranes, wherein the membrane bundle is used for generating a biological membrane on the surfaces of the hollow fiber membranes by hydrogen supply autotrophic denitrification PHA synthesis functional flora; the liquid storage tank is operationally communicated with the membrane bundle and is used for storing an inorganic carbon denitrification culture solution for selectively enriching and culturing the functional flora from sludge; wherein the hydrogen-autotrophic denitrifying PHA synthesis functional flora is used for carrying out nitrogen removal and carbon reduction on sewage and generating PHA, and comprises one or more of hydrogen-autotrophic denitrifying PHA synthesis bacteria, hydrogen-autotrophic denitrifying bacteria, hydrogen-autotrophic acid-producing bacteria, heterotrophic denitrifying bacteria and heterotrophic PHA synthesis bacteria. According to the method, organic combination of a wastewater nitrate nitrogen removal process and PHA synthesis is realized for the first time, and the subversive conversion from carbon emission to carbon fixation is realized by using CO2 as a unique carbon source."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请涉及基于氢能的反硝化耦合聚羟基脂肪酸酯的反应器、反应系统及方法。该反应器包括：由多根聚丙烯聚氨酯复合中空纤维膜组成的膜束，用于供氢自养型反硝化PHA合成功能菌群在所述中空纤维膜的表面上生成生物膜；与膜束操作性地连通的储液罐，其存储有用于从污泥中选择性富集培养该功能菌群的无机碳反硝化培养液；其中，氢自养型反硝化PHA合成功能菌群用于对污水进行脱氮和降碳并生成PHA，包括氢自养型反硝化PHA合成菌、氢自养型反硝化菌、氢自养型产酸菌、异养型反硝化菌、异养型PHA合成菌中的一种或多种。本发明首次实现废水硝态氮去除工艺和PHA合成的有机结合，并利用CO2作为唯一碳源实现从碳排放到碳固定的颠覆性转变。"
                }
            ]
